snippet.title: Game Boy Advance Longplay [027] Kingdom Hearts: Chain of Memories (Sora: Part 1 of 9)
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played By: RickyC

Re: Chain of Memories wasn't released here so until i get a good enough PC to run it the GBA version will do. Not big fan of game but did like riku's story more. I dont use much tactics in battle, I just wanted to get the story. -
